  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study the investigators will recruit patients with the diagnosis of schizophrenia
      that are taking atypical neuroleptics and that are willing to participate in an exercise and
      diet program. The investigators will measure weight and abdomen circumference.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
